
How to set up code and start demo
1. Check out code from GitHub Repository "https://github.com/kuldeeparyadotcom/Centrlized_Logging_Solution_Demo"
2. Execute the start up script "StartCentralizedLoggingDemo"
3. Deploy the Shipper code to hosts where you want to collect logs from
4. On Remote hosts start the Shipper by executing script "StartShipper"

How to stop Centrazlied Logging Solution Demo
1. Stop all the containers running using script "StartCentralizedLoggingDemo  StopCentralizedLoggingDemo"
2. Stop Shipper container on all remote hosts using script "StopShipper"
